summary: This Mod adds Trap Doors to unexplored Worlds...
descriptionHtml:
[u][b]DESCRIPTION:[/b][/u]
This Mod simply makes it easier to reach the Testinteriors which were made by Bethesda.
These rooms are just \"test rooms\".

Outside of Whiterun (see image/map) you can find some trap doors which teleport you to these rooms.
Also included: the Hall from Sovngarde


[u][b]FAQs:[/b][/u]
[b]Q:[/b] Will more testrooms be added?
[b]A:[/b] Only the existing testrooms by Bethesda will be added. (I know, there are still a few testrooms out there)

[b]Q:[/b] Is it compatible with other mods?
[b]A:[/b] As long as there are no other mods in this area, there should be no problem.
author: Dusa
